from aaronc aaron bryce cardena subject re jacob and esau jek write i write that the apostle paul in roman speak of god a choose jacob over esau and add that thi be not a a result of anything that either child have do since they have not be bear yet it my understand that roman a it be write jacob have i love but esau have i hat refer not to the two individual but rather to their offspring the tribe of jacob and the tribe of esau see obadiah for example in fact if you scan through the ot you will find similar reference to the two tribe aaron cardena aaronc 